(1, 'About Garuda Technologies ', 'about-images/images-1-1779307827.jpg', '<h3>Who We Serve</h3><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Business Type</strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p><strong>What Garuda Delivers</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Startups</p></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Early-stage companies needing a digital foundation: website, SEO, and brand identity built for growth from day one.</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>SMEs</p></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Growing businesses ready to scale organic traffic, automate marketing, and build systems that work without daily oversight.</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Enterprises</p></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Large IT firms and corporates requiring multi-domain SEO governance, cloud infrastructure, and complex web application development.</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Individual &amp; Corporate Travelers</p></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p>Leisure travelers, business travelers, and corporate accounts booking flights, hotels, cruises, and car rentals across India and internationally.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><h3>What Sets Garuda Technologies Apart</h3><p>•   Headquartered in Udyog Vihar, Sector 19, Gurugram — Gurgaon&#039;s core IT and industrial corridor.<br>•   2+ years of focused execution with no legacy process overhead slowing delivery.<br>•   IT and travel services delivered under one team — reducing vendor coordination complexity for clients.<br>•   Every IT engagement reports on organic sessions, leads, and revenue — not keyword rankings alone.<br>•   24/7 availability at +91-9910844235 for travel bookings and IT infrastructure emergencies.</p>', 'Gurgaon\'s IT and Travel Partner — Two Verticals. One Accountable Team.', '<p>Garuda Technologies is a Gurgaon-based technology and travel services company. Two verticals operate under one roof: a full-stack IT and digital solutions division covering SEO, web development, app development, cloud infrastructure, and digital marketing — and a travel services division delivering flight booking, hotel reservations, cruise packages, and car rentals through seven specialist travel brands.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Businesses working with Garuda Technologies gain a single point of accountability for their digital presence and travel needs. No juggling multiple vendors. No misaligned priorities. Every service — from ranking a website on Google to booking a business class flight — is managed by one team with one standard of delivery.</p>', 'about-images/images-2-1779307617.webp', 'about-images/images-3-1779307034.webp', 2, 'Our Mission', 'To deliver IT and travel solutions that produce measurable outcomes — not activity reports. Every service Garuda Technologies provides is evaluated against one standard: did it move the client\'s business forward in a way they can see and verify?', 'Our Vision', 'To be the most trusted IT and digital solutions partner for businesses in Gurgaon and Delhi NCR, and the most reliable travel services provider in the Gurugram market — recognized for transparency, technical depth, and consistent delivery.', 'What We Do — Two Verticals, One Standard of Excellence', '<h3>IT and Digital Solutions</h3><p>The IT division covers the complete spectrum of technology and marketing services that businesses need to build, grow, and sustain their digital presence. Services span 10 categories with over 60 individual service offerings:</p><ul><li><p><strong>SEO Services</strong> - 16 sub-services including <strong>Local SEO, Ecommerce SEO, Enterprise SEO, SaaS SEO, Healthcare SEO, AI SEO/GEO, Technical SEO,</strong> and <strong>SEO Consulting</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Digital Marketing</strong> - Including sub-services <strong>Performance Marketing,</strong> <strong>B2B Lead Generation, Google Ads, Meta Ads, PPC, Email Marketing, Content Marketing,</strong> and <strong>Social Media Marketing</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Web Development </strong>- Including sub-services <strong>Custom Website Development, WordPress, Shopify, React, Laravel, PHP, CMS, Corporate Websites, Landing Pages,</strong> and<strong> Web Applications.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>App Development </strong>- Including sub-services <strong>Android, iOS, Flutter, React Native, Enterprise App Development, Web Apps,</strong> and <strong>App Maintenance.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Cloud and DevOps </strong>- Including sub-services <strong>DevOps Consulting, AWS, Google Cloud, Microsoft Azure, Server Management, Cloud Migration,</strong> and <strong>Managed Cloud Services.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Ecommerce Services</strong> - Including sub-services<strong> Ecommerce Website Development, WooCommerce, Magento, Ecommerce Marketing, Payment Gateway Integration,</strong> and <strong>Inventory Management.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>B2B IT Solutions</strong> - Including sub-services <strong>IT Consulting, CRM Development, ERP Development, Enterprise Software, Business Automation, Helpdesk,</strong> and <strong>Custom Business Portals.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Hosting and Infrastructure</strong> - Including sub-services <strong>Web Hosting, VPS, Cloud Hosting, Business Email, Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, SSL, DNS Management,</strong> and <strong>Website Maintenance.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>UI/UX Design</strong> - Including sub-services <strong>UI/UX Design, Wireframing, Prototyping, Website UI, Mobile App UI, and Dashboard Design.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Branding and Creative</strong> - Including sub-services <strong>Logo Design, Brand Identity, Graphic Design, Social Media Creatives, Video Editing, Corporate Branding,</strong> and <strong>Packaging Design.</strong></p></li></ul>', 'about-images/images-4-1779144484.jpg', 'About Garuda Technologies | IT & Travel Company Gurgaon', 'Garuda Technologies is a Gurgaon-based IT and travel solutions company. Learn about our mission, team, services, and why 50+ businesses trust us for digital growth and travel.', '[\"about Garuda Technologies\",\"IT company Gurgaon about\",\"Garuda Technologies team\",\"digital solutions company Gurgaon\",\"travel company Gurugram\",\"about us IT Gurgaon\"]', '2026-04-17 15:30:55', '2026-05-20 14:56:17');

