(1, 'Contact Us', 'contact_images/contact-us-1779222233.jpg', '9910844235', ' info@garudatechnologies.co.in', 'Plot No, 750, Udyog Vihar Phase V Rd, Phase V, Udyog Vihar, Sector 19, Gurugram, Haryana 122016', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d56098.54364837594!2d77.0089244842529!3d28.504864261900998!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d19a576bb7aa9%3A0x6b6ca1dfa56714f3!2sGaruda%20Technologies!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1776555419660!5m2!1sen!2sin\"', '#', '#', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/garuda-technologies-593359382/', 'Contact Garuda Technologies | Gurgaon IT & Travel Company', 'Contact Garuda Technologies in Gurgaon for IT services, SEO, web development, and travel bookings. Call +91-9910844235 or email info@garudatechnologies.co.in for a free consultation.', '[\"contact Garuda Technologies\",\"IT company contact Gurgaon\",\"SEO company contact Gurugram\",\"travel booking contact Gurgaon\",\"Garuda Technologies phone number\",\"IT services contact\"]', '2026-04-18 18:10:30', '2026-05-19 14:53:53');

