INSERT INTO `faqs` (`id`, `question`, `answer`, `is_active`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2, 'What does Garuda Technologies do?', 'Garuda Technologies is a Gurgaon-based IT and travel services company. The IT division provides SEO, digital marketing, web development, app development, cloud and DevOps, ecommerce services, B2B IT solutions, hosting, UI/UX design, and branding across 60+ individual service offerings. The travel division offers flight booking, hotel reservations, cruise packages, and car rental through seven specialized travel brands: Globalairhub, Zippoair, Tripsomaker, Airoflighticket, Airotrolly, Businessclassflyts, and Globalairticketing.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:06:40', '2026-05-18 14:06:40'),
(3, 'Where is Garuda Technologies located?', 'Garuda Technologies is headquartered at Plot No. 750, Udyog Vihar Phase V Rd, Phase V, Udyog Vihar, Sector 19, Gurugram, Haryana 122016. The office is approximately 3 km from Udyog Vihar Metro Station on the Delhi Metro Yellow Line.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:06:53', '2026-05-18 14:06:53'),
(4, 'What are Garuda Technologies\' business hours?', 'Office hours are Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 6:30 PM IST. The phone line at +91-9910844235 is available 24/7 for travel booking support and IT emergency queries outside office hours.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:07:06', '2026-05-18 14:07:06'),
(5, 'Does Garuda Technologies work with clients outside Gurgaon?', 'Yes. While headquartered in Gurgaon, Garuda Technologies serves clients across Delhi NCR, Mumbai, Bangalore, Hyderabad, and other Indian cities, as well as international clients requiring SEO for global markets, web development, and travel services for international destinations. All IT services are delivered remotely with video call-based project management.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:07:23', '2026-05-18 14:07:23'),
(6, 'How long does SEO take to show results?', 'Technical SEO improvements produce measurable Search Console changes within 2 to 4 weeks. Ranking movement on target keywords typically begins between weeks 6 and 12. Competitive head terms in Gurgaon\'s IT and digital services sector require 6 to 12 months of sustained work for top-3 placement. SaaS and healthcare SEO follow similar timelines, with BOFU content pages often producing qualified leads within 60 to 90 days of going live.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:07:35', '2026-05-18 14:07:35'),
(7, 'What is included in a technical SEO audit?', 'Garuda Technologies\' 200-point technical SEO audit covers crawlability and robots.txt configuration, indexation quality and coverage report analysis, Core Web Vitals performance (LCP, INP, CLS) across mobile and desktop, site architecture and internal link depth mapping, schema markup validation, redirect audit (broken links, chains, loops), JavaScript rendering for SPA and headless sites, mobile usability and mobile-first indexing compliance, HTTPS and security headers, and structured data implementation gaps.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:07:46', '2026-05-18 14:07:46'),
(8, 'Do you offer AI SEO and GEO services?', 'Yes. Garuda Technologies provides Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) services alongside traditional SEO. GEO optimizes content structure so that AI systems — ChatGPT, Google Gemini, Perplexity AI, and Claude — cite your brand in their generated responses. Services include AI visibility auditing (testing your brand\'s current citation status across AI platforms), answer-first content restructuring, FAQPage schema implementation, entity consistency standardization, and third-party authority building for training data presence.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:07:58', '2026-05-18 14:07:58'),
(9, 'What digital marketing services do you offer beyond SEO?', 'Beyond SEO, Garuda Technologies provides Google Ads management, Meta (Facebook and Instagram) Ads management, PPC campaign management across Google and LinkedIn, email marketing and automation, content marketing and editorial strategy, social media marketing, performance marketing for B2B lead generation, video marketing, and YouTube channel marketing. All paid media services include weekly optimization and monthly reporting tied to leads and pipeline, not just impressions and clicks.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:08:09', '2026-05-18 14:08:09'),
(10, 'Which technologies does Garuda Technologies use for web development?', 'The web development team works across React, Laravel, PHP, WordPress, Shopify, and custom CMS platforms. Technology selection is driven by the client\'s specific requirements: React for SPA and headless frontend builds, Laravel for complex backend API development, WordPress for content-driven business sites with SEO requirements, and Shopify for ecommerce stores targeting Indian and global markets.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:08:21', '2026-05-18 14:08:21'),
(11, 'How long does a website development project take?', 'A standard 5 to 10 page corporate website takes 3 to 6 weeks from requirement sign-off to live deployment. A custom ecommerce store takes 6 to 12 weeks depending on catalog size and integration complexity. A complex web application or enterprise SaaS product takes 3 to 6 months. Timeline estimates are confirmed in the project Statement of Work after a detailed requirements discussion.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:08:31', '2026-05-18 14:08:31'),
(12, 'Do you provide website maintenance after launch?', 'Yes. Garuda Technologies offers ongoing website maintenance packages covering security updates, performance monitoring, backup management, content updates, and technical support. Maintenance engagements are available as monthly retainers with response time commitments of 1 hour for critical issues and 4 hours for standard support requests.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:08:55', '2026-05-18 14:08:55'),
(13, 'How do I book a flight or hotel through Garuda Technologies?', 'Call +91-9910844235 or email info@garudatechnologies.co.in with your travel dates, destination, number of passengers, and preferred cabin class or hotel category. A travel consultant will respond with fare options and booking confirmation within 2 to 4 hours for standard requests, and within 30 to 60 minutes for urgent last-minute bookings via phone.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:09:07', '2026-05-18 14:09:07'),
(14, 'What travel brands does Garuda Technologies operate?', 'Garuda Technologies operates seven travel brands: Globalairhub (international flights), Zippoair (domestic and international budget tickets), Tripsomaker (holiday packages), Airoflighticket (budget fares and last-minute deals), Airotrolly (full-service business travel management), Businessclassflyts (premium cabin bookings), and Globalairticketing (group and corporate travel). Each brand specializes in a specific traveler segment for better pricing and service quality.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:09:17', '2026-05-18 14:09:17'),
(15, 'Does Garuda Technologies offer corporate travel accounts?', 'Yes. Corporate accounts receive GST-compliant invoicing, consolidated monthly billing, negotiated fare access, and a dedicated travel manager for all bookings. To set up a corporate account, contact the team at +91-9910844235 with your company name, GST number, and estimated monthly travel volume.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:09:28', '2026-05-18 14:09:28'),
(16, 'What is your refund policy for cancelled flights or hotels?', 'Refunds for flight and hotel cancellations are governed by the respective airline\'s or hotel\'s fare rules and cancellation policies. Garuda Technologies applies for refunds on your behalf promptly upon cancellation request. Airline refund processing typically takes 7 to 90 days depending on the airline and payment method. Service fees charged by Garuda Technologies for booking management are non-refundable. Corporate accounts may have additional terms per their account agreement.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:09:37', '2026-05-18 14:09:37'),
(17, 'How does Garuda Technologies price its IT services?', 'IT services are priced based on scope, complexity, and duration. SEO retainers range from INR 15,000 per month for basic local SEO to INR 1,50,000 or more per month for enterprise technical SEO with content production. Web development projects are priced per project based on requirements. Contact the team for a scoped proposal — every quote begins with a free audit or discovery call to understand your specific situation before any number is presented.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:09:49', '2026-05-18 14:09:49'),
(18, 'Do you provide GST invoices?', 'Yes. All Garuda Technologies engagements — IT services and travel bookings — include GST-compliant invoices with GSTIN details for input tax credit eligibility. Corporate accounts receive consolidated monthly invoices covering all bookings and services in the billing period.', 1, '2026-05-18 14:10:02', '2026-05-18 14:10:02');

